* `Draft → Active` requires: no placeholders, schema validation pass, preflight pass, required fields complete, blind-man-safe completeness pass, explicit truth-surface mapping, and no unresolved contradiction between topology mode and declared paths
* `Active → Frozen` requires: acceptance criteria satisfied, evidence recorded, promotion rules satisfied, and follow-on build registration updated if unresolved dual-topology work remains
